  "description": "This quiz assesses JavaScript proficiency by testing knowledge of language features ranging from ES2015 to ES2022 through multiple‑choice questions. It is positioned at an intermediate difficulty, offering a casual, encouraging tone that invites learners to prove their skills without any registration hurdles.",
